            "stanza_text": "On a soupé chez Formosa :\nLa mode est à la poésie.\nOn verra nourris d'ambroisie\nLes rimeurs qu'on martyrisa."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Quoi ! les beaux vers qu'on méprisa,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Maintenant on s'en rassasie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "On a soupé chez Formosa :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "La mode est à la poésie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quoi ! les beaux vers qu'on méprisa,\nMaintenant on s'en rassasie !\nOn a soupé chez Formosa :\nLa mode est à la poésie."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi nous pourrons, sans visa,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
