                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Et Shakspere et Kalidasa !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "On a soupé chez Formosa.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ainsi nous pourrons, sans visa,\nAdmirer à la frénésie\nHugo, dont l'esprit s'extasie,\nEt Shakspere et Kalidasa !\nOn a soupé chez Formosa."
